snippet.title: Longplay of 3 Choume no Tama: Tama and Friends - 3 Choume Obake Panic!!
snippet.description:
Longplay of 3 Choume no Tama: Tama and Friends - 3 Choume Obake Panic!!, played as the NTSC-J version on the Game Boy. This game's version was released on Aug. 5th, 1994. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!
